\f0\fs24 \cf0 This file will give short descriptions for all of the scripts contained in the folder \'93objectMotion\'94, as well as a simple protocol for carrying out the experiment.\
Written By Hope Lutwak. Email hlutwak@nyu.edu with any questions.\
\
Files (all matlab scripts use Psychtoolbox, VisTools):\
calculate_cloud_flow.m - calculate optic flow field in deg/s for a fixating, translating observer based on depth map, motion path placement, translation, view distance to screen, fixation distance\
calculate_cloud_flow_screen.m - same as calculate_cloud_flow but velocity in m/s\
control_3dsetup.m - control experiment\
\
