Protocol:\
TO DO once in each experimental script:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	1)	}Set number of trials per staircase. This is the the number of trials per condition. There are 12 total conditions: for envelope and phase there is translation only, real eye movement to the right and left, and simulated eye movement to the right and left. For timestamp there is only simulated eye movement to the right and left.\
{\listtext	2)	}Decide how many training sessions are needed and how many of the 12 cases to run consecutively.\
{\listtext	3)	}Locate the matlab file for the linearized gamma table in order to calibrate with the monitor that is being used. Place it in the \'93OpticFlow\'94 folder, and change the name of the file in the code. Set \'93linearize\'94 to 1.\
{\listtext	4)	}Change the data path for files to be saved.\
{\listtext	5)	}Change the size of the \'93view_window\'94 to match the dimensions of the monitor used.\
